{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d08147a381","title":"给孙科的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9e3e112608","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":5,"articleId":"d08147a381"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5cf532fa2c","type":"paragraph","text":"给孙科的信！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d08147a381"},{"id":"efee8375a7","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月5日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d08147a381"},{"id":"cd4c4ffdd9","type":"paragraph","text":"今日天下之人莫不属望国民抗日，然国民党中如不战胜其降日派与妥协派则抗日不可能，因此天下之人莫不展望于国民党中之抗日派能有计划地有步骤地向着降日妥协之辈进行坚决之斗争。进行此种斗争，非有有组织的政治力量不可，非有领袖不可，因此天下之人又莫不属望于哲生先生。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d08147a381"},{"id":"1a1d2f1cc3","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东致孙科信的主要内容。孙科（1891-1973），字哲生，广东中山人，孙中山之子。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d08147a381"}],"page":{"id":"d1c74a3772","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"d08147a381","start":148,"end":148}}}},"__N_SSG":true}